chart.name: Top Hosts by Write Ops/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_n_tup_c.ins', filter=filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).sum(by=['host']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('pg_n_tup_c.upd', filter=filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).sum(by=['host']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = data('pg_n_tup_c.del', filter=filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).sum(by=['host']).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (A+B+C).mean(by=['host']).top(count=5).publish(label='D')

chart.name: Blocks Read/sec 7d Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_blks.heap_read', filter=filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('pg_blks.idx_read', filter=filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).timeshift('1w').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B).timeshift('1w').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = ((A-C)/C*100).publish(label='E')
F = ((B-D)/D*100).publish(label='F')

chart.name: Database Size
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_db_size', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-postgresql-9.3-0') and filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).mean().publish(label='A')
B = (A).timeshift('1h').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = ((A-B)/B*100).publish(label='D')
E = ((A-C)/C*100).publish(label='E')

chart.name: Scans/sec 7d Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_scan.seq', filter=filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('pg_scan.idx', filter=filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).timeshift('1w').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B).timeshift('1w').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = ((A-C)/C*100).publish(label='E')
F = ((B-D)/D*100).publish(label='F')

chart.name: Transactions/sec 7d Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_xact.commit', filter=filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('pg_xact.rollback', filter=filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).timeshift('1w').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B).timeshift('1w').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = ((A-C)/C*100).publish(label='E')
F = ((B-D)/D*100).publish(label='F')

chart.name: # Rows 7d Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_n_tup_g.live', filter=filter('host', 'integration-test-postgresql-9.3-0') and filter('plugin', 'postgresql')).mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).timeshift('1w').publish(label='B', enable=False)
